b'Oki ni Mesu mama': b'An original song by Eve, sung by Hatsune Miku, animated by Waboku. Eve\'s self-cover uses the same animated footage and was released on November 29, 2017. Eve included his self-cover MV on his own self-made record label harapeco records\'s CD+DVD release on December 13, 2017 as a part of his "Bunka" album.'
